Package: libr4d-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libr4d0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Remote For Device-under-test Helper Library (development files)
 Remote For Device-under-test (R4D) Daemon acts as controlling server for test
 racks.
 Each rack must contain a serial device server and a power control switch.
 libr4d connects to a R4D Daemon via a SOAP interface to control the connected
 device-under-test.
 .
 This package contains the C library's development files.

